    "is_good_patch": true,
    "synth_pr": "\n## Title: Add missing error logging in GUTI reallocation complete message handling\n\n### Summary\nThe `encode_guti_reallocation_complete` and `decode_guti_reallocation_complete` functions were missing critical error logging for buffer validation failures, making debugging difficult when these functions fail downstream.\n\n### Changes\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/EMM/MSG/GutiReallocationComplete.c`: \n  - Added explicit buffer validation with proper error logging\n  - Replaced macro-based validation that suppressed errors in production builds\n  - Maintained same error codes but now with visible logging\n  - Added nas_log.h include for logging functionality\n\n### Reproduction\nWhen the GUTI reallocation complete message processing fails due to NULL buffer or insufficient buffer length, no error messages were logged in production builds, making it difficult to diagnose issues. Now these critical failures are properly logged with descriptive error messages.\n"
}